<div class="post">
<div class="inner" id="msg_1120892"><span style="font-size: 13pt;" class="bbc_size"><em>这条巨大飞蛇的虹彩鳞片犹如蛋白石一样闪闪发光，炽焰在它燃烧的翅膀的羽毛周围舞动。&nbsp; </em></span><br><hr /><span style="font-size: 14pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: brown;" class="bbc_color"><strong> 忒尔特利羽蛇，CR 14</strong></span></span><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>XP 38400</strong></span><br><br>中立善良 超大型异界生物（本地）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>先攻</strong></span> +8；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感官</strong></span> 黑暗视觉120呎，侦测秩序/混乱/善良/邪恶；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>察觉</strong></span> +30<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>防御</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>AC</strong></span> 30，碰触 13，措手不及 25 （+4敏捷，+1闪避，+17天生，-2体型）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>HP</strong></span> 200（16d10+112）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>强韧</strong></span> +12，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>反射</strong></span> +16，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>意志</strong></span> +17<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>免疫：</strong></span>火焰；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>抗性：</strong></span>强酸 15，寒冷 15， 电击 15；&nbsp; <span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>SR：</strong></span>25<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>攻击</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>速度</strong></span> 30尺，飞行120尺（机动性不良）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>近战</strong></span> 噬咬+25 （2d8+11/19-20 附加摄抓与毒素）， 2 翼击+20（1d8+5 附加燃烧与煽动火焰）<br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">占据</span></strong> 15尺 <strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">触及</span></strong> 15尺<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>类法术能力</strong></span>（施法者等级12 专注+18）<br>恒定—侦测混乱，侦测邪恶，侦测善良，侦测秩序<br>随意使用—侦测思想 (DC 17)，幻化灵体，隐形术, 异界传送（DC 22）<br>1次/每日—阳炎爆<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊攻击</strong></span> 吐息(50尺锥形，12d6火焰 反射DC25减半 冷却1d4轮) 紧勒（2d8+11 附加燃烧）<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>数据</strong></span></span><br><hr /><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>已知术士法术 （施法者等级12 专注+18）</strong></span><br>6环—（4/日）圣言（DC 22）<br>5环—（6/日）驱逐术（DC 21），焰击术<br>4环—（7/日）反制邪恶（DC 20），圣光击，火墙术<br>3环—（7/日）昼明术，解除魔法，火球术（DC 19），灼热光辉（DC 19）<br>2环—（8/日）严加斥责，鹰之威仪，炽焰法球（DC 18），造风术，灼热射线（DC 18） <br>1环—（8/日）燃烧之手（DC 17），魅惑人类，通晓语言，防护邪恶，魔法飞弹<br>0环（随意）—舞光术，晕眩术，侦测魔法，闪光术，光亮术，法师之手，阅读魔法，提升抗力，传讯术<br><br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>力量</strong></span> 32，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>敏捷</strong></span> 19，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>体质</strong></span> 24，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>智力</strong></span> 17，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>感知</strong></span> 24，<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>魅力</strong></span> 23<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>BAB</strong></span> +16；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMB</strong></span> +29（+33擒抱）；<span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>CMD</strong></span> 44（无法被绊摔）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>专长</strong></span> 警觉（Alertness），闪避（Dodge），施法免材（Eschew Materials），盘旋(Hover)，精通重击：噬咬（Improved Critical ：Bite）， 精通先攻(Improved Initiative), 精通要害打击（Improved Vital Strike），闪电反射（Lightning Reflexes），要害打击（Vital Strike）<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>技能</strong></span> 唬骗 +25，飞行 +15，威吓 +25，知识（奥秘）+22，知识（位面）+22，察觉 +30，察言观色 +30，法术辨识 +19，隐匿 +15 <br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>语言</strong></span> 天界语，通用语，龙语；心灵感应100尺<br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力</strong></span> 圣炎（Holy Fire）,毒素<br><hr /><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size"><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong>特殊能力</strong></span></span><br><hr /><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>圣炎（Holy Fire）:</strong></span> 忒尔特利羽蛇造成的火焰伤害，包括它的吐息武器和施展的法术法术，都注入了神圣能量。 这种攻击的一半伤害是火焰伤害，但另一半来自于神圣力量，因此不会被火焰抗力减免。在克服伤害减免时，忒尔特利羽蛇造成的火焰伤害被视为善良阵营。 <br><br><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color"><strong>毒素（EX）：</strong></span>噬咬伤害; 强韧检定 DC 25; 频率 每分钟一次，持续10分钟; 效果 1d6 力量伤害; 连续通过两次检定则治愈。此毒素DC基于体质。<br><br><strong><span style="color: navy;" class="bbc_color">法术：</span></strong>忒尔特利羽蛇可以如12级术士一样施展法术，它也可以施展来自审判者与圣武士法术列表的法术就如这些在术士的法术列表内一样。对于忒尔特利羽蛇而言这些神术被视为奥术，这意味着它不需要法器来施展法术。 <br><br>在所有羽蛇中，忒尔特利羽蛇是最具报复心和最强破坏力的，它们会用正义之怒驱散格拉利昂的诸多邪恶势力。 虽然其它一些羽蛇可能会为邪恶的存在带来救赎，但忒尔特利羽蛇拒斥拯救，并对那些自以为罪行可以得到赦免的派系施加惩罚。忒尔特利羽蛇不会追捕个人，而是针对帮派、腐败的政府，甚至是它们认为已经无法挽救的整个定居点。<br><br>忒尔特利羽蛇的外形令人畏惧。 它的翅膀总是笼罩在火焰中，从根部的温暖橙色到尖端的炽热蓝色，这使得羽蛇周围的空气也会放射出一种不祥的光芒，仿佛末日来临。 同时，羽蛇的乳白色鳞片也似乎反射出神圣的光芒。 典型的忒尔特利羽蛇长35尺，翼展25尺。 它是最重的羽蛇之一，重近6,000磅。 <br><br><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">生态</span></strong></span><br><br>即使与其他羽蛇相比，忒尔特利羽蛇也与穹苍的力量也有着独特的联系。忒尔特利之火的神圣力量如此之强，以至于它可以突破由火焰构成的生物的防御，它的火焰充斥着神圣的力量，可以对邪恶的异界生物、龙和不死生物造成毁灭性的破坏。<br><br>忒尔特利羽蛇很少将它们的神圣羽毛赠送给凡人，但是当它们这样做时，这意味着真正的荣誉，并且会赋予羽毛的接受者巨大的力量。忒尔特利羽蛇所给予的羽毛在所有其它方面都等同于（克特莎）羽蛇的羽毛，允许施法者将其用作额外的材料成分来在施展异界盟友时召唤特定的忒尔特利羽蛇，而无需花费一般的黄金或其他贵重物品作为报酬——前提是忒尔特利羽蛇同意实行施法者所要求的服务。或者，在施展任何带有火焰描述符的伤害法术时，忒尔特利羽蛇的羽毛也可以用作额外的材料成分；在这种情况下，该法术获得法术极效专长的好处，但是该法术需使用比该法术实际等级高3级的法术位。 <br><br><span style="color: green;" class="bbc_color"><strong><span style="font-size: 12pt;" class="bbc_size">栖息地与社会</span></strong></span><br><br>当一片区域已经充满了不可救药的邪恶时，忒尔特利羽蛇将会作为最后的解决手段出现。充斥着不死生物的鬼城，被邪恶精类困扰的枯萎森林，以及充当魔鬼或恶魔门户的跨位面传送门，都可能成为忒尔特利羽蛇的愤怒的目标。除了崇拜正义的神祇例如莎仑莱和托拉格之外，忒尔特利羽蛇还为不成比例的至高天领主服务，代表强大的天使和亚空（如拉贾瑟尔、奥理翁和戴莫瑞启）执行迅捷的正义。像他们的主人一样，他们扮演着神圣行刑者的角色，对邪恶的代理人实施最极端的惩罚。<br><br>尽管忒尔特利羽蛇几乎在稀有程度上可谓传奇，但那些认出这些强大生物的人很快就会明白即将到来的毁灭。传说在星陨之灾后不久，忒尔特利羽蛇在格拉利昂上变得更为活跃，因为它们努力对抗在这个黑暗时代出现的邪恶。<br><br>如果当一个忒尔特利羽蛇被要求消灭一个不可救药的区域时，羽蛇会招募凡人来帮助它，通常以特使和代表的形式，它们将会为目标的罪人提供最后的救赎机会。然而，忒尔特利羽蛇的特权是惩罚，而非怜悯，任何在错误的时间被忒尔特利羽蛇发现与错误的存在有关联的人都会有祸了。如果在忒尔特利羽蛇所瞄准的群体或定居点中存在真正的无辜者，羽蛇可能会派遣一名使者，例如一个被魅惑的人，以预先警告无辜者，否则它会毫不犹豫地将整个区域焚毁。它们侍奉的神祇非常了解忒尔特利羽蛇那无与伦比的报复倾向，因此他们通常会派遣其他羽蛇或天使之类的天族伴随忒尔特利羽蛇，以确保能够在将定居点毁灭期间撤离或保护无关者。 <br><br><div style="margin:20px; margin-top:5px"><div class="smallfont" style="margin-bottom:2px"><b>剧透</b> - &nbsp;<i> </i>: <input type="button" value="顯示" style="width:60px;font-size:10px;margin:0px;padding:0px;" onClick="if (this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display != '') { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = ''; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;this.innerText = ''; this.value = '隐藏'; } else { this.parentNode.parentNode.getElementsByTagName('div')[1].getElementsByTagName('div')[0].style.display = 'none'; this.innerText = ''; this.value = '显示'; }"></div><div class="alt2" style="margin: 0px; padding: 6px; border: 1px inset;"><div style="display: none;">Couatl, Tletli<br>This massive flying serpent’s iridescent scales glimmer like opals, and white-hot flames dance along the feathers of its burning wings.<br>Tletli CR 14<br>Source Pathfinder #143: Borne by the Sun&#039;s Grace pg. 84<br>XP 38,400<br>NG Huge outsider (native)<br>Init +8; Senses darkvision 120 ft., detect chaos/evil/good/ law; Perception +30<br>Defense<br>AC 30, touch 13, flat-footed 25 (+4 Dex, +1 dodge, +17 natural, –2 size)<br>hp 200 (16d10+112)<br>Fort +12, Ref +16, Will +17<br>Immune fire; Resist acid 15, cold 15, electricity 15; SR 25<br>Offense<br>Speed 30 ft., fly 120 ft. (poor)<br>Melee bite +25 (2d8+11/19–20 plus grab and poison), 2 wings +20 (1d8+5 plus burn and stoke fire)<br>Space 15 ft., Reach 15 ft.<br>Special Attacks breath weapon (50-ft. cone, 12d6 fire, Reflex DC 25 half, usable every 1d4 rounds), burn (2d6 fire, DC 25), constrict (2d8+11 plus burn)<br>Spell-Like Abilities ((CL 12th; concentration +18))<br>Constant—detect chaos, detect evil, detect good, detect law<br>At will—detect thoughts (DC 17), ethereal jaunt, invisibility, plane shift (DC 22)<br>1/day—sunburst (DC 24)<br>Spells Known (CL 12th; concentration +18)<br>6th (4/day)—holy word (DC 22)<br>5th (6/day)—dismissal (DC 21), flame strike<br>4th (7/day)—dispel evil (DC 20), holy smite, wall of fire<br>3rd (7/day)—daylight, dispel magic, fireball (DC 19), searing light (DC 19)<br>2nd (8/day)—castigate (DC 18), eagle’s splendor, flaming sphere (DC 18), gust of wind (DC 18), scorching ray<br>1st (8/day)—burning hands (DC 17), charm person (DC 17), comprehend languages, magic missile, protection from evil<br>0 (at will)—dancing lights, daze (DC 16), detect magic, flare (DC 16), light, mage hand, message, read magic, resistance<br>Statistics<br>Str 32, Dex 19, Con 24, Int 17, Wis 24, Cha 23<br>Base Atk +16; CMB +29 (+33 grapple); CMD 44 (can&#039;t be tripped)<br>Feats Alertness, Dodge, Eschew MaterialsB, Hover, Improved Critical (bite), Improved Initiative, Improved Vital Strike, Lightning Reflexes, Vital Strike<br>Skills Bluff +25, Fly +15, Intimidate +25, Knowledge (arcana) +22, Knowledge (planes) +22, Perception +30, Sense Motive +30, Spellcraft +19, Stealth +15<br>Languages Celestial, Common, Draconic; telepathy 100 ft.<br>SQ holy fire<br>Ecology<br>Environment any<br>Organization solitary, pair, or revelation (3–6 plus 1–2 angels and 1 chicome couatl)<br>Treasure standard<br>Special Abilities<br>Holy Fire (Su) Fire damage dealt by a tletli, including that of its breath weapon and spells, is infused with divine energy. Half the damage of such attacks is fire damage, but the other half is the result of holy power and thus not subject to being reduced by resistance to fire-based attacks. Fire damage dealt by a tletli is considered good-aligned for the purpose of overcoming damage reduction.<br><br>Poison (Ex) Injury—bite; save Fort DC 25; frequency 1/minute for 10 minutes; effect 1d6 Str; cure 2 consecutive saves.<br><br>Spells A tletli casts spells as a 12th-level sorcerer, and can cast spells from the inquisitor and paladin spell lists as well as those normally available to a sorcerer. These divine spells are considered arcane spells for the tletli, meaning that the creature does not need a divine focus to cast them.<br><br>Stoke Flames (Ex) Once per round when a tletli attacks with its wings, it can cause areas of active fire within 30 feet to spread as a free action. An affected 5-foot square of fire spreads to one adjacent square that is not on fire, possibly burning objects or creatures in that space. The tletli determines which adjacent squares are set on fire.<br>Description<br>Of all the couatls, tletlis are among the most vengeful and easily the most actively destructive, channeling their righteous fury to rid Golarion of large swaths of evildoers. While some couatls may offer redemption to evil individuals, a tletli withholds salvation and exacts punishment on whole sects of people whose crimes they deem warrant oblivion. Tletlis do not hunt down individuals, instead targeting gangs, corrupt governments, and even entire settlements that they believe have fallen beyond redemption.<br><br>The tletli is a terrifying sight to behold. Its wings are continually shrouded in flame, ranging from warm orange at the base to hot blue at the tips, causing the air around the couatl to radiate with an ominous light best described as apocalyptic. Further magnifying the effect, the beast’s opalescent scales seem to reflect a divine light. A typical tletli is 35 long with a wingspan of 25 feet. It is one of the heaviest couatls, weighing nearly 6,000 pounds.<br>Ecology<br>The tletli has a unique connection to the powers of the firmament, even compared to other couatls. The divine intensity of a tletli’s fire is so great that it can penetrate the defenses of even creatures made from flame, and its conflagration is infused with holy power that can wreak devastation among evil outsiders, dragons, and undead.<br><br>Tletlis rarely gift their sacred feathers to mortals, but when they do it is a true honor, and one that bestows great power upon the recipient of the holy item. A tletli’s freely given feather acts in all ways as a couatl’s feather, allowing a spellcaster to use it as an additional material component to cast planar ally to conjure that specific tletli without expending the typical payment of gold or other valuables—provided the tletli approves of the service asked for by the spellcaster. Alternatively, a tletli’s feather can be used as an additional material component while casting any damage-dealing spell with the fire descriptor; in this case, the spell gains the benefits of the Maximize Spell metamagic feat, and the spell uses up a spell slot 3 levels higher than the spell’s actual level.<br>Habitat and Society<br>A tletli appears only as a last resort, when a particular settlement or area has become filled with irredeemably evil individuals. Ghost towns overrun with undead, blighted forests plagued by evil fey, and interplanar portals that act as gateways for devils or demons are all likely targets for a tletli’s wrath. In addition to their worship of righteous deities such as Sarenrae and Torag, tletlis serve a disproportionate number of empyreal lords, enacting swift justice on behalf of mighty angels and archons like Ragathiel, Olheon, and Damerrich. Like their masters, they assume the role of divine executioners, meting out the most extreme discipline possible to agents of vileness.<br><br>Although tletlis are near legendary in terms of their scarcity, those who recognize these massive creatures for what they are quickly understand the destruction soon to come. Legend tells that tletlis were more prominent on Golarion shortly after Earthfall as they worked to fight the evils that arose during the Age of Darkness.<br><br>If and when a tletli is called upon to obliterate an irredeemable region, the couatl enlists mortals to aid its efforts, typically in the form of envoys and delegates who extend a final chance for redemption to the sinners in question. A tletli’s prerogative, however, is punishment, not mercy, and woe be unto any who cavort with the wrong kind of company at the wrong time in a tletli’s presence. If there are genuine innocents within a group or settlement on which the tletli has set its sights, the couatl may send an emissary, such as a charmed person, to forewarn the pure of heart, but it otherwise does not hesitate to incinerate the entire locale. Their deific masters understand tletlis’ unrivaled propensity for holy retribution all too well, and they typically send other couatls or celestials like angels to accompany the tletlis in case there are a number of individuals in a settlement that should be evacuated or protected during the razing.</div></div></div></div>
